title.narrative: New Element

description.narrative: Satisfactory progress was made at strategic level, including supporting the Global Action Plan on Child Wasting, and operational level. UNICEF continued enhancing access to and delivery of quality nutrition services, supported the finalization of strategic and legislative documents including the Nutrition Strategic Plan and decree-law for improved nutrition outcomes and to protect, promote and support infant and young child feeding (IYCF) practices. Supported the community mobilization through Mother Support Groups (MSG) to adopt recommended nutrition practices and advocacy for integration of nutrition supplies into the essential medicine list and nutrition response to the victims of April 2021 floods. | Status:Met | As-of Date:30/12/2021
